&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4">&lt;code class="language-shell" data-lang="shell">debian &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff">9&lt;/span>
/var/log 通用日志
/etc 通用配置文件
修改ssh端口
/etc/ssh/sshd_config
/etc/ssh/ssh_config
service ssh restart
查看占用
netstat -lnp | grep ss-server
查看进程
ps -ax | grep ss-server
结束PID对应的进程
kill -9 &lt;span style="color:#f92672">[&lt;/span>PID&lt;span style="color:#f92672">]&lt;/span>
查找文件
find . -name &lt;span style="color:#e6db74">&amp;#34;*.json&amp;#34;&lt;/span>
查看所有端口使用
netstat –apn
netstat -anp|grep &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff">80&lt;/span>
查看80端口使用
lsof -i:80
结束nginx
pkill -9 -f nginx
后台挂起运行
nohup xxxxxx &amp;amp;
下载文件
scp -r root@0.0.0.0: /folder /localfolder
&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div></description></item><item><title>Docker之常用命令</title><link>/posts/docker%E4%B9%8B%E5%B8%B8%E7%94%A8%E5%91%BD%E4%BB%A4/</link><pubDate>Tue, 17 Oct 2017 22:17:38 +0800</pubDate><guid>/posts/docker%E4%B9%8B%E5%B8%B8%E7%94%A8%E5%91%BD%E4%BB%A4/</guid><description>&lt;p>常用命令&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>Localhost设置https</title><link>/posts/localhost%E8%AE%BE%E7%BD%AEhttps/</link><pubDate>Thu, 14 Sep 2017 19:46:57 +0800</pubDate><guid>/posts/localhost%E8%AE%BE%E7%BD%AEhttps/</guid><description>&lt;h1 id="证书生成">证书生成&lt;/h1></description></item><item><title>Nginx取消304缓存</title><link>/posts/nginx%E4%B9%8B%E7%A6%81%E6%AD%A2%E7%BC%93%E5%AD%98/</link><pubDate>Mon, 14 Nov 2016 20:07:30 +0800</pubDate><guid>/posts/nginx%E4%B9%8B%E7%A6%81%E6%AD%A2%E7%BC%93%E5%AD%98/</guid><description>&lt;p>加上这个这个配置&lt;/p></description></item></channel></rss>